Sentencas: Powder Injection Molding (PIM) gives the possibility to produce, at an industrial rate, ceramic parts with fine details.
Titulo: Fabrication of structured anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell by powder injection molding

Sentencas: It is thus a possible approach to reduce the fabrication costs of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Fabrication of structured anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell by powder injection molding

Sentencas: This work presents fabrication and electrochemical characterization results of injection-molded structured anode-supported SOFCs.
Titulo: Fabrication of structured anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell by powder injection molding

Sentencas: Planar anode-supported SOFCs with fine details have been produced by injection molding of a mixture of nickel oxide (NiO) and yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ).
Titulo: Fabrication of structured anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell by powder injection molding

Sentencas: The channeling structure and support porosity ensure gas transport on the fuel side.
Titulo: Fabrication of structured anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell by powder injection molding

Sentencas: Initial anode support characterizations like sintering shrinkage, porosity and electrical conductivity have been done on simple Ni-YSZ test bars.
Titulo: Fabrication of structured anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell by powder injection molding

Sentencas: Thin YSZ electrolyte has been deposited by spin-coating on the PIM green body before half-cell co-sintering.
Titulo: Fabrication of structured anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell by powder injection molding

Sentencas: Electrochemical testing was carried out with a lanthanum-strontium manganite (LSM)-YSZ cathode.
Titulo: Fabrication of structured anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell by powder injection molding

Sentencas: The performance is comparable to tape-cast anode-supported cells, with 0.45 W cm(-2) obtained at 0.6 V and 810 degrees C. Medium-term galvanostatic testing shows a degradation rate of about 1.1% kh(-1).
Titulo: Fabrication of structured anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell by powder injection molding

Sentencas: Post-test analysis with scanning electron microscopy (SEM) and energy dispersive X-ray spectroscopy (EDS) attribute this mainly to cathode degradation due to Cr and S poisoning.
Titulo: Fabrication of structured anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell by powder injection molding

Sentencas: These results are therefore promising for using a PIM fabrication process in the SOFC field.
Titulo: Fabrication of structured anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell by powder injection molding
